<h3 id="intelligent-album-manager">Intelligent Album Manager</h3>
<p>Many people make photo albums of their family or close friends or relatives but have a hard time finding photos of particular people which they want or to sort them according to that.<br>
Here, our application comes into work, where you can simply choose some photos as a collection of all the different faces available in the album and sort all the photos at once by the face detected in each photo. The application is purely based on the AWS Rekognition client (and its services) and AWS S3 ( Storage).</p>
<p>The basic working of the application is to take a source image and compare it with all the faces in the collection to find a match, as soon as we get a match, the program will put that particular photo in the folder of the person whose face was detected. Itâ€™ll run in a loop until we get all our photos sorted, all we need to do is just upload the photos and ask our Intelligent Album Manager to do its magic.</p>
